first solo set.

05:43.076 --> 05:45.379
I love it. Good stuff, X.

05:45.413 --> 05:46.480
Thank you.

05:46.514 --> 05:47.748
BECKY:
Good stuff?

05:47.781 --> 05:49.917
That makes zero sense.
Both Hakeem

05:49.950 --> 05:51.419
and Tiana
have albums dropping

05:51.452 --> 05:53.387
before Nessa.
Yeah, but I'm
your boss.

05:53.421 --> 05:56.490
Andre is mine,
so just do the math.

05:56.524 --> 05:58.559
HAKEEM:
Here's some math.

05:58.592 --> 06:00.894
I have as many voting shares
on the board as Andre.

06:00.928 --> 06:02.763
(laughs)

06:02.796 --> 06:04.565
ANDRE: Well, the board
is not involved

06:04.598 --> 06:07.100
in the day to day
of the company, Hakeem.

06:07.134 --> 06:10.904
Cookie wants Tiana,
so that's what she's gonna get.

06:10.938 --> 06:12.039
Pop.

06:16.444 --> 06:17.445
So...

06:17.478 --> 06:19.012
vote on the table is whether

06:19.046 --> 06:21.415
to feature Nessa or Tiana
at the showcase.

06:21.449 --> 06:23.417
Yo, are you hardheaded
or stupid?

06:23.451 --> 06:24.785
