06:30.658 --> 06:33.126
It's Nessa
that gets the showcase.

06:33.160 --> 06:34.962
Dad, wait, you can't
be doing this.

06:34.995 --> 06:36.229
End of story.

06:42.636 --> 06:44.171
We're done here.

06:48.175 --> 06:50.944
Hey, Becky, listen.
You can save your sorrys,

06:50.978 --> 06:52.813
Xavier, I don't want them.

06:52.846 --> 06:56.450
No, you come at me in front
of the bosses like that again,

06:56.484 --> 06:58.151
I will fire you.

07:00.253 --> 07:02.155
How's that sorry for you?

07:07.160 --> 07:10.397
All right, so I'm-a hit you
when I land in Boston.

07:10.430 --> 07:11.799
You really have to go, huh?

07:11.832 --> 07:12.800
Yeah.

07:12.833 --> 07:15.235
I hope this Jayce plays ball.

07:15.268 --> 07:16.804
I mean, they got
all the files, right?

07:16.837 --> 07:17.971
Including the
citation from

07:18.005 --> 07:19.573
when they pulled me
over for that DUI.

07:19.607 --> 07:22.309
That alone doesn't place me
anywhere near that lake

07:22.342 --> 07:23.977
where Carla drowned.

07:24.011 --> 07:25.713
Carla.

07:28.849 --> 07:31.184
(scoffs) You know what?

07:31.218 --> 07:33.821
I couldn't even
remember her name

07:33.854 --> 07:36.323
till I saw it
in that file.

07:36.356 --> 07:38.826
I mean, I just met the girl
at that party that night.

07:38.859 --> 07:41.028
It was... (sighs)

07:41.061 --> 07:42.896
She seemed like
she was nice.

07:44.131 --> 07:46.166
And Jayce?

07:46.199 --> 07:48.502
Jayce, I didn't know him
that well, either.

07:48.536 --> 07:50.337
I mean, went to
grade school together.

07:50.370 --> 07:54.107
He ended up doing six years
for involuntary manslaughter.

07:54.141 --> 07:56.810
The arrest records
are sealed, but...

07:58.411 --> 08:00.347
...nobody from school
ever heard from him,

08:00.380 --> 08:02.282
so if I could
just get him

08:02.315 --> 08:04.818
to make a
statement, then...

08:06.386 --> 08:08.288
You know what,
don't worry about me.

08:08.321 --> 08:11.792
You got a lot on your
plate with Jamal.

08:11.825 --> 08:13.694
You see your boy
today, huh?

08:13.727 --> 08:15.228
You excited
to see Jamal?

08:15.262 --> 08:17.531
It's the first time
since I put him in rehab.

08:17.565 --> 08:18.999
That's right.

08:20.067 --> 08:23.070
I'm so scared, Angelo.
I just...

08:23.103 --> 08:26.540
I want my baby back,
healthy, sober and strong.

08:26.574 --> 08:27.741
I know.

08:27.775 --> 08:30.210
You will.

08:30.243 --> 08:33.647
Hey, just believe in him.

08:33.681 --> 08:34.882
All right?

08:34.915 --> 08:37.084
All right?

08:39.086 --> 08:40.888
Okay.
You look good.

08:40.921 --> 08:43.256
Thank you. (chuckles)

08:48.028 --> 08:49.730
Good afternoon.

08:49.763 --> 08:52.165
I'm Dr. Katz.
I'm Jamal's therapist.

08:52.199 --> 08:53.667
How's Jamal doing?

08:53.701 --> 08:55.168
We'll wait for him to tell you.

08:55.202 --> 08:57.104
Excuse me, do you have
a sound system in here?

08:57.137 --> 08:59.239
I want my brother to hear some
new stuff I've been working on.

08:59.272 --> 09:02.175
I'm afraid you'll have to wait
another three weeks until...

09:02.209 --> 09:05.579
TORY: Sunny Day Recovery Center
doesn't believe in music.

09:05.613 --> 09:08.348
Just one of the many stupid
rules at this dire refugee camp.

09:08.381 --> 09:10.183
Tory, this is a private
family session.

09:10.217 --> 09:11.752
Yo, Tory Ash.

09:11.785 --> 09:13.754
Yo, Hakeem Lyon.

09:13.787 --> 09:15.122
Oh, and Andre.

09:16.657 --> 09:18.592
And the mama bear Lyon herself.

09:18.626 --> 09:19.760
What's up, Cookie?

09:19.793 --> 09:21.361
Tory.
TORY: Relax, cornball.

09:21.394 --> 09:23.096
I'm just saying hello.

09:23.130 --> 09:24.865
From what Jamal's told me,

09:24.898 --> 09:27.000
I'm surprised all your little
Lyon cubs aren't in rehab.

09:29.236 --> 09:31.605
Don't try me, little girl,
not today.

09:31.639 --> 09:33.273
Please.
Oh, Cookie, I could try you,

09:33.306 --> 09:35.275
but I think I'd rather wait
and try Lucious instead.

09:35.308 --> 09:37.945
Oh, yeah, you should do that,
'cause you'll stay alive.

09:37.978 --> 09:40.681
I already told you
he's not coming.

09:42.816 --> 09:44.151
I see y'all met

09:44.184 --> 09:46.053
my crazy-ass friend, Tory.

09:46.086 --> 09:47.988
Good luck.
Thank you.

09:48.021 --> 09:50.290
Hey, Ma.
Jamal. (sighs)

09:50.323 --> 09:51.324
(chuckles)

09:53.426 --> 09:55.162
You look good. (chuckles)
Thanks, Mom.

09:55.195 --> 09:56.897
What's up, bro?
What's up, brother?

09:56.930 --> 09:58.565
(Cookie chuckles)

09:58.598 --> 09:59.566
What's up, Dre?

09:59.599 --> 10:00.968
Damn. Tory Ash.

10:01.001 --> 10:02.636
The whole world

10:02.670 --> 10:03.837
