what happened to her

10:03.871 --> 10:05.238
ever since she stripped
butt naked

10:05.272 --> 10:06.807
onstage at Fenway Park.

10:06.840 --> 10:09.677
Show some respect, Hakeem.
The woman has an illness.

10:09.710 --> 10:11.812
Yeah, you would know a lot
about that, wouldn't you?
COOKIE: Shut up, boy.

10:11.845 --> 10:15.015
Yeah, she was a big star.
I mean, brilliant, too.

10:15.048 --> 10:17.017
Yeah.
That heroin knocked her ass
right out the sky.

10:17.050 --> 10:18.485
She had that meltdown
at Fenway.

10:18.518 --> 10:22.489
Didn't they find her in a coma
at some dingy motel?

10:22.522 --> 10:25.759
Mrs. Lyon, I have to ask you
not to indulge in gossip

10:25.793 --> 10:27.260
about other the residents.

10:27.294 --> 10:29.997
Sorry.

10:30.030 --> 10:31.364
Now, should we wait

10:31.398 --> 10:32.933
for Mr. Lyon, or...?

10:32.966 --> 10:34.668
Uh, like Jamal said,

10:34.702 --> 10:35.936
his father
ain't coming.

10:35.969 --> 10:37.037
LUCIOUS:
His father is what?

10:38.405 --> 10:40.540
How's my boy?
JAMAL: Dad.

10:40.573 --> 10:42.009
Look at you,

10:42.042 --> 10:44.377
all bright-eyed
and strong

10:44.411 --> 10:45.913
and ready for the world.

10:47.547 --> 10:51.685
How's my boy doing recovering
from those addictive drugs

10:51.719 --> 10:53.353
his mama got
him hooked on?

10:53.386 --> 10:56.256
Lucious, if you gonna be here,
can you be here for the family?

10:57.557 --> 11:00.360
That's rich,
coming from you.

11:00.393 --> 11:02.029
DR. KATZ:
I'm sure Jamal is happy

11:02.062 --> 11:03.563
that his whole family is here.

11:04.898 --> 11:06.800
Jamal,

11:06.834 --> 11:08.869
do you want to tell them
what's on your mind

11:08.902 --> 11:10.537
at the halfway point?
Sure.

11:10.570 --> 11:12.906
(clears throat)
Um, well...

11:14.607 --> 11:16.309
...first week was
absolute hell.

11:16.343 --> 11:19.079
I don't ever want to go
through withdrawal again.

11:19.112 --> 11:20.413
And we know you won't, bro.

11:21.581 --> 11:24.051
Yeah, if you stay clean.

11:24.084 --> 11:25.719
COOKIE: What do
you mean, "if"?

11:25.753 --> 11:27.755
He is clean.

11:27.788 --> 11:29.723
Right, Jamal?
Completely clean.

11:29.757 --> 11:31.391
You know, that's...

11:31.424 --> 11:33.026
that's why
I want to go home.

11:34.094 --> 11:35.562
What?
I need to go home.

11:35.595 --> 11:38.231
I got this...
this melody that's in my head.

11:38.265 --> 11:39.933
It's been pushing me the entire
time that I've been here,

11:39.967 --> 11:41.268
and I need to get
to the studio

11:41.301 --> 11:43.370
and I need to lay it down
before I lose it.

11:45.973 --> 11:49.009
So, your body is
healed, I get that,

11:49.042 --> 11:50.911
but you need to stay
and finish this program.

11:50.944 --> 11:53.180
Okay, Ma,
I need to finish the program.

11:53.213 --> 11:55.615
I also need to finish
the pills in the drain.

11:59.286 --> 12:00.687
I'm sorry, Ma,
that was messed up.

12:00.720 --> 12:02.122
That wasn't fair to you,
I'm sorry.

12:05.292 --> 12:08.328
I gave you those pills because
I saw you were in pain, Jamal.

12:10.063 --> 12:11.765
No, tell the truth.

12:11.799 --> 12:13.967
You gave him those pills
because you needed him

12:14.001 --> 12:15.969
to perform at that event.

12:16.003 --> 12:18.772
You also was conflicted
because you had to choose

12:18.806 --> 12:20.941
between the needs
of your boyfriend

12:20.974 --> 12:22.943
or the needs of your son.

12:22.976 --> 12:25.445
You don't know what
he did to Angelo.
What I did to Angelo...

12:25.478 --> 12:27.114
Mr. and Mrs. Lyon...
COOKIE:
Would you shut the hell up?

12:27.147 --> 12:28.648
LUCIOUS:
It's not half as bad as

12:28.681 --> 12:31.284
what you did to Empire
and to Empire's name.

12:31.318 --> 12:33.720
